Class DynamicArrowPropertyValue

java.lang.Object

wtf.choco.arrows.api.property.DynamicArrowPropertyValue
All Implemented Interfaces:
ArrowPropertyValue
public class DynamicArrowPropertyValue
extends SimpleArrowProperty
Represents an ArrowPropertyValue that gets recomputed every time it is fetched. Useful for configuration-based values.

Parker Hawke - Choco
